  "prompt": "What is the best family car I can buy for a budget of 100K english pounds ?",
  "response": "With a budget of \u00a3100,000, you have access to a wide range of high-quality family cars that combine luxury, practicality, and performance. Here are some of the best options:\n\n### 1. **Tesla Model X**\n   - **Price**: Starting around \u00a385,000\n   - **Highlights**: All-electric, cutting-edge technology, Falcon Wing doors, seating for up to 7, impressive range, and autopilot features.\n   - **Why It\u2019s Great**: Perfect for eco-conscious families, with ample space and futuristic design.\n\n### 2. **Volvo XC90 Recharge Plug-In Hybrid**\n   - **Price**: Starting around \u00a370,000\n   - **Highlights**: Luxurious interior, excellent safety features, seating for 7, and a powerful plug-in hybrid engine.\n   - **Why It\u2019s Great**: A stylish, safe, and practical SUV with a strong focus on sustainability.\n\n### 3. **Audi Q7**\n   - **Price**: Starting around \u00a365,000\n   - **Highlights**: Premium build quality, spacious interior, advanced tech, and powerful engine options.\n   - **Why It\u2019s Great**: A versatile and luxurious SUV with a reputation for reliability and performance.\n\n### 4. **BMW X5**\n   - **Price**: Starting around \u00a365,000\n   - **Highlights**: Sporty handling, luxurious interior, advanced infotainment system, and a range of engine options.\n   - **Why It\u2019s Great**: Combines luxury with performance, making it a great choice for families who enjoy driving.\n\n### 5. **Land Rover Range Rover Sport**\n   - **Price**: Starting around \u00a375,000\n   - **Highlights**: Iconic design, off-road capability, luxurious interior, and advanced tech.\n   - **Why It\u2019s Great**: A premium SUV that offers both on-road comfort and off-road prowess.\n\n### 6. **Mercedes-Benz GLE**\n   - **Price**: Starting around \u00a365,000\n   - **Highlights**: Luxurious cabin, advanced safety features, spacious interior, and a range of powerful engines.\n   - **Why It\u2019s Great**: A well-rounded SUV that offers luxury, comfort, and performance.\n\n### 7. **Porsche Cayenne**\n   - **Price**: Starting around \u00a365,000\n   - **Highlights**: Sporty performance, luxurious interior, advanced tech, and a range of powerful engine options.\n   - **Why It\u2019s Great**: A high-performance SUV that doesn\u2019t compromise on luxury or practicality.\n\n### 8. **Lexus RX 450h**\n   - **Price**: Starting around \u00a360,000\n   - **Highlights**: Hybrid powertrain, luxurious interior, excellent reliability, and advanced safety features.\n   - **Why It\u2019s Great**: A reliable and efficient luxury SUV with a focus on comfort and quality.\n\n### 9. **Jaguar F-PACE**\n   - **Price**: Starting around \u00a350,000\n   - **Highlights**: Stylish design, sporty handling, luxurious interior, and advanced tech.\n   - **Why It\u2019s Great**: A sleek and stylish SUV that offers a blend of performance and luxury.\n\n### 10. **Kia EV9 (Upcoming)**\n   - **Price**: Expected around \u00a370,000\n   - **Highlights**: All-electric, spacious interior, cutting-edge tech, and seating for 7.\n   - **Why It\u2019s Great**: A futuristic and eco-friendly option with Kia\u2019s renowned value and reliability.\n\n### Key Considerations:\n- **Space**: Ensure the vehicle has enough seating and cargo space for your family.\n- **Safety**: Look for advanced safety features and high crash test ratings.\n- **Technology**: Consider the infotainment system, connectivity options, and driver-assistance features.\n- **Fuel Efficiency**: If you\u2019re eco-conscious, consider hybrid or electric options.\n- **Resale Value**: Some brands and models hold their value better than others.\n\nUltimately, the best family car for you will depend on your specific needs, preferences, and priorities. Test driving a few options can help you make the best decision.",
  "temperature": 1.0,
